          <img alt=""
       src="https://developers.google.cn/web/billions/images/cost.png"
       srcset="https://developers.google.cn/web/billions/images/cost_36.png 36w,https://developers.google.cn/web/billions/images/cost_48.png 48w,https://developers.google.cn/web/billions/images/cost_72.png 72w,https://developers.google.cn/web/billions/images/cost_96.png 96w,https://developers.google.cn/web/billions/images/cost_480.png 480w,https://developers.google.cn/web/billions/images/cost_720.png 720w,https://developers.google.cn/web/billions/images/cost_856.png 856w,https://developers.google.cn/web/billions/images/cost_960.png 960w,https://developers.google.cn/web/billions/images/cost_1440.png 1440w,https://developers.google.cn/web/billions/images/cost_1920.png 1920w,https://developers.google.cn/web/billions/images/cost_2880.png 2880w"
       sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, (max-width: 840px) 50vw, 708px">
  
  </figure>
  </div>


        <div class="devsite-landing-row-item-description"
         >

      

      <div class="devsite-landing-row-item-body">
        
                    <h3 id="">
      减少流量消耗</h3>
    
    

                  <div class="devsite-landing-row-item-description-content">
            与较差的连接相比，高昂的流量费用通常会给用户带来更大的障碍。移动用户极具费用意识；在漫游或产生意外费用时，即使是“无限制”流量计划，费用也会变得极高。许多移动用户都对费用非常在意，而他们的理由十分充分： 在印度，500MB 流量计划需要花费 17 小时的最低小时工资。

          </div>
        
        
                  <div class="devsite-landing-row-item-buttons">
      <a href="/web/fundamentals/design-and-ux/responsive/content#weight"
      class="wf-small-link
      "
            >了解加载页面和应用组件的开销</a>    <a href="/web/fundamentals/performance/optimizing-content-efficiency"
      class="wf-small-link
      "
            >减少交互所需的数据量</a>    <a href="/web/fundamentals/getting-started/principles#home-page-and-site-navigation"
      class="wf-small-link
      "
            >简化导航：帮助用户快速获取所需信息</a>    <a href="/web/fundamentals/performance/critical-rendering-path"
      class="wf-small-link
      "
            >设置内容显示的优先级</a></div>
              </div>
    </div>
      
</div>
